{"tid":2202545,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國被揭發有個監察網遍佈全球，收集個人資料全部送中","createTime":"2020-09-14T15:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T11:20:32.000Z","uid":261647,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ff6d9095ea2bb579a412f8d3fcf0d4fabf1bb1c2","tid":2202545,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/3533035163402858/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.907682852604782%2F3533035163402858%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacb7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=fad2ed94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/3533035163402858/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n中國被揭發有個監察網遍佈全球，收集個人資料全部送中，集齊環球各政軍學商同專業重要人士（包埋家人）於一資料庫，總共有二百四十萬人嘅詳細紀錄！由於真係太大，依家只係拆咗十分一出嚟：<br />\n／Of the 250,000 records recovered, there are 52,000 on Americans, 35,000 Australians, 10,000 Indian, 9,700 British, 5,000 Canadians, 2,100 Indonesians, 1,400 Malaysia and 138 from Papua New Guinea.<br />\n<br />\nThere are 793 New Zealanders profiled in the database, of whom 734 are tagged of special interest or politically exposed.／<br />\n<br />\n唔止係爬公開資料，仲有私密資料附加&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n／While much of the information has been &quot;scraped&quot; from open-source material, some profiles have information which appears to have been sourced from confidential bank records, job applications and psychological profiles.<br />\n<br />\nThe company is believed to have sourced some of its information from the so-called &quot;dark web&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nOne intelligence analyst said the database was &quot;Cambridge Analytica on steroids&quot;, referring to the trove of personal information sourced from Facebook profiles in the lead up to the 2016 US election campaign.／<br />\n<br />\n外國人自嘆不如，依家深切反省&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n&quot;I think it speaks to the broader threat of what China is doing and how they are surveilling, monitoring and seeking to influence&hellip; not just their own citizens, but citizens around the world.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;In the process, the company has violated the privacy of millions of global citizens, the terms of service of just about every major social media platform and hacked other companies for their data.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n之前爆出中國反對 TikTok 賣盤，依家睇番轉頭，頗堪玩味&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n9月12日：中國據報反對賣TikTok 寧願關閉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2581322/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2581322%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacb7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=eb1dbf29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2581322/</a><br />\n<br />\n#中國又成最大贏家<br />\n#ChinaNumberOne<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/abcnews/status/1305220869946445824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabcnews%2Fstatus%2F1305220869946445824&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacb7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=3833692f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fabcnews%2Fstatus%2F1305220869946445824&h=30ca2ca6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/abcnews/status/1305220869946445824</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awubUCO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawubUCO.png&h=02b8d3d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"619f6b076db9bcc676a1a15193b5bb845e957d1f","tid":2202545,"uid":55913,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"PR公司都對應唔嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b23b7512b0b8c6fb825886be58b41031fe95307","tid":2202545,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:49:35.000Z","msg":"深圳一家私營企業被揭在全球大肆收集個人資料，再售予國家機構。涉事的深圳振華數據被指同解放軍有聯繫，其積累達 240 萬人的數據庫中，包括數以萬計知名與具影響力人士的詳細個人資料，而該數據庫相信被中國情報部門使用。事件被譽為「劍橋分析 (Cambridge Analytica) 嚴重版」。 <br />\n<br />\n振華數據成立於 2018 年，相信由中國振華電子集團持有，該集團是中國電子信息產業集團有限公司和貴州省國資委控股的國營企業。<br />\n<br />\n振華數據的主要客戶包括解放軍和中國共產黨；該公司收集的數據有出生日期、地址、婚姻狀況、照片，政治聯繫、親戚和社交媒體帳戶，甚至會整合個人 Twitter 、 Facebook 、 LinkedIn 、 Instagram 甚至 TikTok 帳戶內容，以及新聞報道、犯罪和公司記錄。"},{"pid":"20bc205b54fc0e3114b4f580dcffca7f79c3d261","tid":2202545,"uid":313615,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:50:58.000Z","msg":"網絡安全公司 Internet 2.0 ，該公司成功將該數據庫的 10% 解碼，發現當中有 5.2 萬個美國人、 3.5 萬個澳洲人、 1 萬個印度人、 9,700 個英國人、 5,000 個加拿大人的資料，亦有數以千計的印尼、馬來西亞以及巴布亞新畿內亞人個人數據。<br />\n<br />\n目前該數據庫已與美國、加拿大、英國、意大利、德國和澳洲的國際媒體聯盟共享"},{"pid":"380bd634df672550802368176f5704bd58c291af","tid":2202545,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"振華數據在全球約有 20 個「收集點」，將大量數據傳送回中國；現時已確定其中兩個點位於美國堪薩斯州和南韓首爾，澳洲很大可能有一個收集點，但仍在調查之中。<br />\n<br />\nPotter 指，振華數據已經建立了跟蹤海軍艦艇和國防資產、評估軍官職業和對中國競爭對手的知識產權進行分類的能力。振華數據似乎對軍方數據特別有興趣，並追蹤官員和政治網絡的人事升遷事宜。一位美國海軍軍官的晉升受到嚴密監控，被標示為未來核航空母艦司令。<br />\n<br />\n數據庫包含多名國際知名人士，包括，英女皇、英國王儲查理斯王子（Prince Charles）、澳洲科技大亨 Mike Cannon-Brookes、歌手 Natalie Imbruglia 等。據澳洲廣播公司 (ABC) 報道，澳洲有 35,558 個被收集個人資料的澳洲人包括政客、軍官、外交官、學者、企業高層、新聞工作者等，現任與前任首相的資料也有被收集。當中 656 人被列入「特殊利益」或「高知名度」名單中，數據庫未有標示這兩個類別的含義，而名單上的人在職業和背景上是完全不同，亦無解釋為何這些人會被列在名單中。"},{"pid":"6a9cb2c8a2c6e5d9f03e6aa8c50ac5d9710535e2","tid":2202545,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />five eye收網"},{"pid":"f12aceb23250c895fd713201b9a76fbf5d5d3490","tid":2202545,"uid":313615,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:53:09.000Z","msg":"澳方指雖然大部分資料都是從開放源中取得，但某些個人檔案中的資料似乎來自機密的銀行記錄、工作申請和當局調查所得的心理檔案。振華數據亦被指從所謂的「暗網 (dark web) 」取獲取部份個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n一位情報分析師向澳洲廣播公司表示，該數據庫比 2016 年劍橋分析 (Cambridge Analytica) 從 Facebook 獲取大量個人資料，更為嚴重。雖然是次的數據庫涉及人數較劍橋分析的 5,000 萬少，但現時情報顯示，振華數據使用了人工智能來追蹤可公開獲取的數據，以建立複雜的全球個人和組織資料庫。"},{"pid":"234579252023bd3e6c3a75100df4263955db5ad2","tid":2202545,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"左膠：what about US gov<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e10f1cdc660d2092bd5b2a7e542a01d6b25060f","tid":2202545,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"今天西方主流媒體都報導了中國深圳振華信息公司大量收集世界各國私人信息新聞。深圳振華信息隸屬中國央企CETC，這次被爆光的信息是內部人員向曾在北大任教的美國教授洩露。深圳振華CEO王雪峰曾在IBM工作，他聲稱支持中共對外發動「混合戰爭」。美國有5萬多人、澳洲有4萬多人私人信息被收集。"},{"pid":"c5a30dd6ef16b84950f26494ce5b3ced5db3e3ea","tid":2202545,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"打鳩中國啦"},{"pid":"bbaed839419e770290bd79d83f17c32411e7972f","tid":2202545,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6a9cb2c8a2c6e5d9f03e6aa8c50ac5d9710535e2","tid":2202545,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />five eye收網"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"等支共收集完，爆佢大鑊，再直接攞料<br />\n錢又唔洗比，又可以整臭佢個名，再落佢面話比人知我一直睇住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b99ce66ad36b64e948e9bc783990bdbdf6b3763","tid":2202545,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bbaed839419e770290bd79d83f17c32411e7972f","tid":2202545,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6a9cb2c8a2c6e5d9f03e6aa8c50ac5d9710535e2","tid":2202545,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor